        "additional_notes": [
            "PU-31 yields 10–12 q/ha, resists MYMV and powdery mildew",
            "Early maturity (75–85 days), determinate growth, medium-sized glossy black seeds",
            "Rhizobium treatment enhances nitrogen fixation, reducing fertilizer needs",
            "High market demand for uniform seeds with quick cooking time, good palatability",
            "Post-harvest drying to 8–10% moisture, pest-resistant storage minimizes losses",
            "Suitable for kharif/summer, rainfed/irrigated conditions in Telangana’s loamy soils",
            "Nitrogen fixation improves soil fertility for crop rotations (e.g., rice-wheat-urdbean)",
